{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 10,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "iJpuSZDxZSBJHFSeavba",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "sister-m"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 448.153,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Jacob, speak unto you again,",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.431,
      "end": 7.75,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.93,
      "end": 11.552,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning this righteous branch of which I have spoken.",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 12.232,
      "end": 15.576,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, the promises which we have obtained",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 15.756,
      "end": 19.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are promises unto us according to the flesh;",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 19.28,
      "end": 21.834,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, as it has been shown unto me",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 22.014,
      "end": 25.265,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that many of our children shall perish in the flesh",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 25.445,
      "end": 27.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of unbelief,",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 27.297,
      "end": 31.105,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, God will be merciful unto many;",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 31.285,
      "end": 33.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and our children shall be restored,",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 33.88,
      "end": 36.852,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may come to that which will give them",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 37.032,
      "end": 39.633,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the true knowledge of their Redeemer.",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 40.313,
      "end": 42.635,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, as I said unto you,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 42.815,
      "end": 49.363,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it must needs be expedient that Christ\u2014",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 49.543,
      "end": 58.924,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for in the last night the angel spake unto me that this should be his name\u2014",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 59.104,
      "end": 61.008,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should come among the Jews,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 61.188,
      "end": 64.625,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among those who are the more wicked part of the world;",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 64.805,
      "end": 70.099,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall crucify him\u2014",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 70.279,
      "end": 72.833,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus it behooveth our God,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 73.013,
      "end": 77.936,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there is none other nation on earth that would crucify their God.",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 78.616,
      "end": 83.028,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For should the mighty miracles be wrought among other nations",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 83.208,
      "end": 87.016,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they would repent, and know that he be their God.",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 87.696,
      "end": 90.668,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But because of priestcrafts and iniquities,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 90.848,
      "end": 94.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they at Jerusalem will stiffen their necks against him,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 94.79,
      "end": 96.508,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he be crucified.",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 97.188,
      "end": 99.742,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, because of their iniquities,",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 99.922,
      "end": 103.359,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "destructions, famines, pestilences,",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 103.539,
      "end": 106.279,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bloodshed shall come upon them;",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 106.459,
      "end": 109.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they who shall not be destroyed",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 109.425,
      "end": 112.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be scattered among all nations.",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 112.891,
      "end": 115.724,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, thus saith the Lord God:",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 115.904,
      "end": 118.737,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "When the day cometh that they shall believe in me,",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 118.917,
      "end": 120.728,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I am Christ,",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 120.908,
      "end": 123.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then have I covenanted with their fathers",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 123.735,
      "end": 127.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall be restored in the flesh, upon the earth,",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 127.955,
      "end": 130.138,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the lands of their inheritance.",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 130.818,
      "end": 135.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall come to pass that they shall be gathered in",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 135.317,
      "end": 139.404,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from their long dispersion, from the isles of the sea,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 139.584,
      "end": 142.185,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and from the four parts of the earth;",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 142.365,
      "end": 147.288,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the nations of the Gentiles shall be great in the eyes of me,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 147.468,
      "end": 148.49,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith God,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 148.67,
      "end": 152.432,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in carrying them forth to the lands of their inheritance.",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 153.112,
      "end": 158.499,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, the kings of the Gentiles shall be nursing fathers unto them,",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 158.679,
      "end": 162.394,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their queens shall become nursing mothers;",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 162.574,
      "end": 167.543,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the promises of the Lord are great unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 167.723,
      "end": 170.974,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he hath spoken it, and who can dispute?",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 171.654,
      "end": 173.604,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, this land,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 173.784,
      "end": 177.406,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "said God,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 177.586,
      "end": 183.763,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be a land of thine inheritance,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 183.943,
      "end": 187.519,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Gentiles shall be blessed upon the land.",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 188.199,
      "end": 192.797,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And this land shall be a land of liberty unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 192.977,
      "end": 195.578,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there shall be no kings upon the land,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 195.758,
      "end": 198.219,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who shall raise up unto the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 198.899,
      "end": 203.218,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will fortify this land against all other nations.",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 203.898,
      "end": 208.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he that fighteth against Zion shall perish, saith God.",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 209.129,
      "end": 213.401,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he that raiseth up a king against me shall perish,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 213.581,
      "end": 215.439,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I, the Lord,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 215.619,
      "end": 217.198,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the king of heaven,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 217.378,
      "end": 218.957,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will be their king,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 219.137,
      "end": 222.248,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I will be a light unto them forever,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 222.428,
      "end": 224.146,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that hear my words.",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 224.826,
      "end": 230.352,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, for this cause,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 230.532,
      "end": 232.808,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that my covenants may be fulfilled",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 232.988,
      "end": 235.635,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have made unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 235.815,
      "end": 239.809,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I will do unto them while they are in the flesh,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 239.989,
      "end": 243.704,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I must needs destroy the secret works of darkness,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 243.884,
      "end": 245.231,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of murders,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 245.411,
      "end": 247.036,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of abominations.",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 247.716,
      "end": 250.642,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, he that fighteth against Zion,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 250.822,
      "end": 252.819,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both Jew and Gentile,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 252.999,
      "end": 254.81,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both bond and free,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 254.99,
      "end": 256.755,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both male and female,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 256.935,
      "end": 258.328,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall perish;",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 258.508,
      "end": 262.548,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they are they who are the whore of all the earth;",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 262.728,
      "end": 266.954,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they who are not for me are against me, saith our God.",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 267.634,
      "end": 273.485,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I will fulfil my promises which I have made unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 273.665,
      "end": 280.538,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I will do unto them while they are in the flesh\u2014",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 281.218,
      "end": 284.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, my beloved brethren, thus saith our God:",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 285.113,
      "end": 288.596,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will afflict thy seed by the hand of the Gentiles;",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 288.776,
      "end": 292.398,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, I will soften the hearts of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 292.578,
      "end": 295.597,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall be like unto a father to them;",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 295.777,
      "end": 298.563,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the Gentiles shall be blessed",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 298.743,
      "end": 301.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and numbered among the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 302.117,
      "end": 305.786,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I will consecrate this land unto thy seed,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 305.966,
      "end": 309.217,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and them who shall be numbered among thy seed,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 309.397,
      "end": 312.23,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "forever, for the land of their inheritance;",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 312.41,
      "end": 314.221,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it is a choice land,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 314.401,
      "end": 316.073,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith God unto me,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 316.253,
      "end": 318.111,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "above all other lands,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 318.291,
      "end": 321.635,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore I will have all men that dwell thereon",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 321.815,
      "end": 324.741,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall worship me, saith God.",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 325.421,
      "end": 327.464,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 327.644,
      "end": 330.895,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "seeing that our merciful God has given us",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 331.075,
      "end": 334.233,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so great knowledge concerning these things,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 334.413,
      "end": 336.131,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "let us remember him,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 336.311,
      "end": 338.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and lay aside our sins,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 338.441,
      "end": 340.949,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and not hang down our heads,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 341.129,
      "end": 343.172,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for we are not cast off;",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 343.352,
      "end": 348.46,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, we have been driven out of the land of our inheritance;",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 348.64,
      "end": 351.194,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but we have been led to a better land,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 351.374,
      "end": 354.068,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Lord has made the sea our path,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 354.248,
      "end": 357.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we are upon an isle of the sea.",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 357.714,
      "end": 361.058,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But great are the promises of the Lord",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 361.238,
      "end": 364.535,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto them who are upon the isles of the sea;",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 364.715,
      "end": 366.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore as it says isles,",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 367.031,
      "end": 369.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there must needs be more than this,",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 369.533,
      "end": 373.016,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they are inhabited also by our brethren.",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 373.696,
      "end": 378.015,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, the Lord God has led away from time to time",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 378.195,
      "end": 379.913,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 380.093,
      "end": 382.694,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to his will and pleasure.",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 382.874,
      "end": 387.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now behold,",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 387.28,
      "end": 391.227,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord remembereth all them who have been broken off,",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 391.407,
      "end": 393.961,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore he remembereth us also.",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 394.641,
      "end": 397.195,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore, cheer up your hearts,",
      "verse": "10:23",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 397.375,
      "end": 404.434,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and remember that ye are free to act for yourselves\u2014",
      "verse": "10:23",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 404.614,
      "end": 409.583,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to choose the way of everlasting death or the way of eternal life.",
      "verse": "10:23",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 410.263,
      "end": 412.539,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 412.719,
      "end": 415.645,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "reconcile yourselves to the will of God,",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 415.825,
      "end": 419.401,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and not to the will of the devil and the flesh;",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 419.581,
      "end": 423.436,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and remember, after ye are reconciled unto God,",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 423.616,
      "end": 428.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it is only in and through the grace of God that ye are saved.",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 429.451,
      "end": 434.141,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, may God raise you from death by the power of the resurrection,",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 434.321,
      "end": 439.197,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also from everlasting death by the power of the atonement,",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 439.377,
      "end": 443.092,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye may be received into the eternal kingdom of God,",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 443.272,
      "end": 446.476,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye may praise him through grace divine.",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 446.656,
      "end": 447.492,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 131
    }
  ]
}